Replaces: python3-griffe
Description: Signatures for entire Python programs (griffelib)
 griffe extracts the structure, frame, and skeleton of your Python project
 to generate API documentation or find breaking changes in your API.
 .
 griffelib is the library distribution of griffe, providing stable
 programmatic access to its core functionality.
 .
 This package provides the Python 3 library (imported as griffe).
